{"tid":177997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警違法被捕增23%     保安局長斥有人肆意抹殺警貢獻","createTime":"2017-03-29T08:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T09:09:11.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84dd0bf82f3393bccc7b912279c547a64df5ca47","tid":177997,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170329/large/1490776975_f22e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F1490776975_f22e.jpg&h=d87e93ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰質詢，去年共43名警務人員犯刑事罪行被捕，較前年上升23%，警隊如何維持誠信。保安局局長黎棟國回覆表示，警隊有三萬多人，涉嫌犯案的只有幾十個。警隊自2009年起已成立警察誠信管理委員會，加強警員誠信。他反指最近不斷有人肆意抹殺警務人員對維持治安的貢獻，對絕大部分盡忠職守的警員不公平。 <br />\n<br />\n民建聯的陳克勤及葛佩帆均批評鄭松泰抹黑紀律部隊，挑撥警民關係，當局應設立辱警罪。黎棟國表示，對於是否設立辱警罪，當局正在探討、搜集資料及研究的階段。"},{"pid":"130a99b72c47c6752b8347afc9edcfb6696b3cc5","tid":177997,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef8d4ebc28c6ba322531e8e3748ac96a03f88c0e","tid":177997,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c10c336c78df845faac44e72c10fd25078808b","tid":177997,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"殺警係貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保安局長想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}